Professional Hair Stylist
Attractive salary Package
5 days per week, including weekends and PH
Islandwide


Job Responsibilities

• Recommending hairstyles and haircuts according to customers’ face shapes and tastes
• Perform professional hair colouring techniques, including ombre highlights, etc.
• Washing, rinsing, cutting, style hair and drying clients’ hair using appropriate shampoos and conditioners (e.g. for oily hair or dry scalps). Apply chemicals to change texture of hair.
• Apply hair treatment products, as needed (e.g. color protection creams and hydrating masks)
• Give clients advice on how to maintain a hairstyle or look,
• Recommending appropriate products and treatments
• Explain the best ways to maintain hair health and why it's importan
• Maintain good relationship with the clients
Job Requirements:

• At least 1 -2 years work experience as a Hair Stylist, Hairdresser, Colorist or similar role
• Knowledge of a wide range of haircuts, suitable for all hair lengths and various coloring techniques
• Up-to-date with industry trends
• Good customer service and communication skills

